load data
   ↓
[Data Loader]
   ├─ CSV → OneHot (N, 105)
   └─ Variable Structure (37 vars → 105 states)
   ↓
[Prior Builder]
   ├─ FCI skeleton → skeleton_mask (105, 105)
   ├─ LLM direction → direction_prior (105, 105)
   └─ Block structure → List[{var_pair, row_indices, col_indices}]
   ↓
[Model Initialization]
   └─ raw_adj (105, 105) ← logit(direction_prior)
   ↓
[Training Loop] × 200 epochs
   ├─ Forward Pass
   │   └─ adjacency = sigmoid(raw_adj) * skeleton_mask
   │   └─ predictions = observations @ adjacency
   │
   ├─ Loss Computation
   │   ├─ L_recon = BCE(predictions, observations)
   │   ├─ L_sparse = Σ_blocks ||W_block ⊙ P_block||_F
   │   └─ L_cycle = Σ_pairs ||W_A→B||_F × ||W_B→A||_F
   │
   └─ Backward Pass
       └─ Update raw_adj via gradient descent
   ↓
[Evaluation]
   ├─ Extract learned edges (threshold = 0.1)
   ├─ Compare with ground truth
   └─ Metrics: Precision, Recall, F1, Orientation Accuracy